- So to satisfy
your desires,

46:12.200 --> 46:13.934
sexual or otherwise,

46:14.000 --> 46:15.700
you...

46:15.767 --> 46:17.166
sacrificed a boy.

46:17.233 --> 46:19.433
- I was convinced that
Adam deserved to get raped.

46:19.500 --> 46:23.567
You know, he raped that girl,
he attacked me.

46:23.633 --> 46:25.700
But when I saw him
in the gym, I...

46:35.100 --> 46:36.934
I realized that no matter
what Adam had done,

46:37.000 --> 46:38.467
no one deserves that.

46:41.233 --> 46:43.567
My guilt is
devouring me.

46:43.633 --> 46:46.000
- So it should.

46:46.066 --> 46:47.433
- What can I do to make
peace with myself?

46:49.333 --> 46:52.066
Well, I could
tell you,

46:52.133 --> 46:53.533
but you wouldn't
want to hear it.

46:54.433 --> 46:56.367
- Go on.

46:56.967 --> 47:00.934
- This calamity was brought on
by your need to see Keller,

47:01.000 --> 47:02.767
so the only way for you
to punish yourself

47:02.834 --> 47:05.500
is by you denying
yourself Keller.

47:05.567 --> 47:06.500
- You mean
don't see him.

47:06.567 --> 47:10.266
- That's right.

47:10.333 --> 47:12.333
- Ever again?

47:12.400 --> 47:13.633
- That's right.

47:17.266 --> 47:19.800
- Christ.

47:19.867 --> 47:23.867
- If you are
truly sorry, Beecher,

47:23.934 --> 47:24.900
that's what
you must do.

47:26.967 --> 47:28.400
- I want to transfer
to another work detail.

47:28.467 --> 47:33.033
- You transferred to the
mailroom not even a week ago.

47:33.100 --> 47:35.767
- Yeah, I'm not enjoying it
as much as I thought I would.

47:35.834 --> 47:37.233
- Is there trouble
with Schillinger?

47:37.300 --> 47:39.533
- No, I just realized
that pushing a cart around

47:39.600 --> 47:40.867
isn't the best use
of my talents.

47:40.934 --> 47:43.033
- Well, Sister Peter Marie's
already replaced you.

47:43.100 --> 47:44.400
- I know.

47:44.467 --> 47:47.333
- The only opening's
in the women's dress factory.

47:47.400 --> 47:49.066
- Fine.
- So wait a second.

47:49.133 --> 47:51.834
Sewing hems on women's dresses
is a better use of your talent?

47:51.900 --> 47:53.467
Don't fuckin'
bullshit me.

47:53.533 --> 47:54.467
What's going on?

47:54.533 --> 47:55.700
- Nothing.

47:55.767 --> 47:57.834
- All right, all right.

47:57.900 --> 48:00.233
This is a prison,
not an employment agency.

48:00.300 --> 48:01.533
We try
to accommodate people,

48:01.600 --> 48:03.200
but we can't always.

48:03.266 --> 48:06.200
Now, you asked to work
in the mailroom.

48:06.266 --> 48:07.467
Until you give me
a legitimate reason

48:07.533 --> 48:08.500
why you can't,

48:08.567 --> 48:09.500
you stay
in the fuckin' mailroom!

48:09.567 --> 48:10.500
Go!

48:20.667 --> 48:23.300
- I have a special delivery
for Dr. Nathan.

48:59.834 --> 49:00.767
- Can I help you?

49:00.834 --> 49:02.834
- Where's Sister Pete?

49:02.900 --> 49:04.567
- In a staff meeting.

49:04.633 --> 49:06.533
- You're that sheriff
from Unit J, right?

49:06.600 --> 49:08.266
- Alvin Yood, yeah.

49:08.333 --> 49:10.000
- Yeah, I'm Tobias Beecher.

49:10.066 --> 49:11.433
- Hey.

49:11.500 --> 49:12.633
- I used to have this job.

49:12.700 --> 49:14.967
- And you gave it up?

49:15.033 --> 49:17.033
Nothing personal,

49:17.100 --> 49:19.200
but you're a dolt.

49:19.266 --> 49:22.467
- Look, when Sister Pete
gets back from her appointment,

49:22.533 --> 49:25.700
can you give her this note
and tell her to make a meeting

49:25.767 --> 49:27.300
with Adam Guenzel?

49:27.367 --> 49:31.266
He's in Unit B, and I think
he needs somebody to talk to.

49:31.333 --> 49:32.667
- About what?

49:32.734 --> 49:34.633
- She'll know
when she sees him.

49:34.700 --> 49:38.133
- Okay, I'll give her
your message.

49:38.200 --> 49:40.300
- Thanks, so long.

49:41.100 --> 49:44.734
- Hey, Beecher,
don't take any wooden nickels.

49:54.700 --> 49:56.166
- How you doing, Adam?

49:56.233 --> 49:58.767
- What do you care?

49:58.834 --> 50:01.500
- Look, I'm sorry
I let them rape you, okay?

50:01.567 --> 50:04.467
But it's this place,
you know.

50:04.533 --> 50:06.300
It got my head
all fucked up.

50:08.166 --> 50:10.834
Mine too.

50:10.900 --> 50:13.700
- We gotta be there
for each other, bro.

50:13.767 --> 50:14.834
- Why?

50:14.900 --> 50:16.433
You want to borrow
my lipstick.

50:16.500 --> 50:21.166
- Guenzel, Sister Peter Marie
has requested your presence.

50:22.834 --> 50:23.967
- What for?

50:24.033 --> 50:26.266
- My guess: to Saran wrap
your brain.

50:31.100 --> 50:34.600
- Hey, prag, come here.

50:34.667 --> 50:35.900
You listen up.

50:35.967 --> 50:37.500
You don't jabber
one fuckin' word to her

50:37.567 --> 50:38.800
about what
we done to you.

50:38.867 --> 50:40.033
- Yes, sir.

50:40.100 --> 50:41.500
- And clean that shit
off your face.

50:51.400 --> 50:53.133
- So that's it.

50:53.200 --> 50:55.367
You have nothing
else to say.

50:55.433 --> 50:57.967
- No, ma'am.

50:58.033 --> 50:59.433
- Tell me about your
relationship

50:59.500 --> 51:01.033
with Tobias
Beecher.

51:01.100 --> 51:03.567
- I don't have a relationship
with Beecher.

51:03.633 --> 51:04.867
- We shared a cell in Em City,
that's all.

51:04.934 --> 51:07.734
- What about when
you were both outside?

51:07.800 --> 51:09.734
- Our families were friendly,
but he's, like,

51:09.800 --> 51:10.900
10 years older than me.

51:10.967 --> 51:13.567
We never hung out
or anything.

51:13.633 --> 51:15.133
- What if I told you

51:15.200 --> 51:17.000
that he's very
concerned about you?

51:17.066 --> 51:19.633
- I'd tell you
he's a lying cocksucker.

51:21.300 --> 51:23.600
I'm sorry for swearing.

51:23.667 --> 51:26.700
- I've heard worse.

51:26.767 --> 51:28.734
Why is he a liar?

51:28.800 --> 51:29.834
- He knows why.

51:29.900 --> 51:31.266
- You don't want
to tell me?

51:31.333 --> 51:32.900
- Ask him.

51:37.467 --> 51:40.233
- Normally, my role in these
sessions is to mediate,

51:40.300 --> 51:43.467
to referee, but...

51:43.533 --> 51:46.266
Today I'm gonna be
a little more aggressive.

51:46.333 --> 51:49.834
Our subject
is Adam Guenzel.

51:49.900 --> 51:51.266
I had a meeting
with Adam Guenzel

51:51.333 --> 51:54.133
when he first
came to Oz.

51:54.200 --> 51:55.600
Since then,

51:55.667 --> 51:58.500
his behavior patterns
have changed significantly.

51:58.567 --> 52:02.000
Clearly he has
been abused sexually

52:02.066 --> 52:05.133
and I suspect that the three
of you know the details.

52:06.100 --> 52:07.734
Tobias?

52:13.266 --> 52:14.633
- He was raped,

52:14.700 --> 52:17.767
gang raped
about a week ago.

52:17.834 --> 52:19.200
- By whom?

52:24.800 --> 52:26.633
- I'm not investigating
this as a crime.

52:26.700 --> 52:30.800
I just want
to help the boy.

52:30.867 --> 52:32.700
Vern.

52:32.767 --> 52:34.567
- I don't know what
you're talking about.

52:37.200 --> 52:39.300
- Said,

52:39.367 --> 52:41.800
can you shed
any light on this?

52:51.166 --> 52:52.200
- No.

52:54.200 --> 52:56.100
- Fine.

52:56.166 --> 52:58.834
But I want you to know
that I am not

52:58.900 --> 53:00.900
letting this pass.

53:01.667 --> 53:04.600
I'm going to be seeing
Adam Guenzel every single day

53:04.667 --> 53:06.333
until I can get him
to open up,

53:06.400 --> 53:09.033
until he can tell me
exactly what happened.

53:09.100 --> 53:10.500
This session is closed.

53:11.867 --> 53:13.033
I am sick

53:13.100 --> 53:14.867
of sitting
in the same room with you.

53:18.667 --> 53:20.934
- Adam Guenzel has
become a liability.

53:21.000 --> 53:22.900
- You think he'll blab
to the nun?

53:22.967 --> 53:25.300
- Uh-huh.

53:25.367 --> 53:26.734
Hey, prag,

53:26.800 --> 53:27.734
get in here.

53:35.233 --> 53:36.500
- Yes, sir?

53:36.567 --> 53:39.667
- I've got good news.

53:39.734 --> 53:40.900
We're gonna
help you escape.

53:59.700 --> 54:01.867
- Beecher,
I've got some news.

54:01.934 --> 54:04.934
Adam Guenzel is dead.

54:05.000 --> 54:06.200
- What?

54:06.266 --> 54:08.300
- They just
found his body.

54:08.367 --> 54:10.567
Evidently he was
climbing the fence,

54:10.633 --> 54:13.266
he was attempting
to escape.

54:13.333 --> 54:14.900
He got
past the barbed wire,

54:14.967 --> 54:15.900
but then the fence...

54:15.967 --> 54:17.166
- He was electrocuted.

54:17.233 --> 54:20.967
- 4,000 volts,
straight through him.

54:21.033 --> 54:23.767
- Fuck.

54:23.834 --> 54:24.934
- I'm sorry.

55:10.300 --> 55:11.667
- So...

55:11.734 --> 55:13.633
that road to Hell that's
paved with good intentions--

55:13.700 --> 55:16.934
I'm not saying
to make a detour,

55:17.000 --> 55:19.200
only that before
you make your first step,

55:19.266 --> 55:21.533
consider the consequences.

55:21.600 --> 55:24.266
Because good
can turn to bad

55:24.333 --> 55:26.900
in the blink
of a fucking eye.
